# {{.Name}} ({{.Type}})

Manages an environment within a Dokploy project. Environments allow you to organize and isolate applications and databases.

## Example Usage

```terraform
resource "dokploy_project" "myproject" {
  name = "My Application"
}

resource "dokploy_environment" "production" {
  name        = "Production"
  description = "Production environment"
  project_id  = dokploy_project.myproject.id
}
```

